(numRobEntries, area_cell_area).explanation: Increasing ROB entries requires more storage cells and associated logic, directly increasing the physical cell area needed for implementation;

(numRobEntries, power_register).explanation: More ROB entries mean more register-like storage elements that consume power for data retention and access operations;

(numRobEntries, nL2TLBEntries).explanation: ROB size and L2 TLB entries serve different functions in the processor pipeline and do not have a direct causal relationship;
